Taranaki wool
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:the tree fungus <i>Auricularia polytricha</i> Hakeka; an old word for the edible jew's ear fungus collected for sale. [from its one-time commercial importance in a mainly dairy-farming area]
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: ear fungus
Pronunciation:
